high_descs: Turn around and walk to the wall on the other side of the room, then turn right and walk to the stove.
Take the skillet from the stove.
Turn right and walk to the sink on the other side of the room.
Put the skillet in the sink, rinse it off, and pick it back up.
Turn around and walk back to the stove.
Put the skillet down on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Replace a dirty skillet from the stove with a clean one.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the stove on your right.
Pick up the dirty pan on the right front burner.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the pan into the sink, wash it then pick it back up.
Turn around and walk back to the stove on your right.
Put the pan back on the right front burner.
Turn around and go to the stove on the left.
Take the pan from the stove.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Place the pan in the sink and run water to wash it.
Take the pan from the sink, turn around, and take it back to the stove on the right.
Place the cleaned pan back on the stove.
